    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied it since day one, kept it garaged, and stayed on top of every single service. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
