    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade example of automotive excellence. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its original showroom luster with a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the deep metallic finish pop. The interior remains in pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery is free of any bolster wear or creasing, and the cabin still carries that signature new-car scent. Every electronic component functions flawlessly, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intuitive driver-assist features. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. It drives with the same precision, tightness, and silence as the day it rolled off the assembly line. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection and a turn-key experience, this is the definitive choice.",
