    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s a total gem. This car has been pampered since day one\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! The paint is flawless, the interior is spotless, and it drives like an absolute dream. I've taken such good care of it, and I'm looking for a new owner who will love it just as much. You really have to see this one in person to believe how perfect it is!",
